title: Unranked to Diamond 5 in 101 games AMA. (1month roughly)
body:
http://oce.op.gg/summoner/userName=Danklight%20Vayne

Wtf that is epic... I'd love to be that good. Eventually.. Highest is gold 5 but recently I've been in great mindset to be as chill as qtpie.. I laugh at screwups now rather then raging so.. One day..
